---
import logo from "../assets/logo-bg-white.png";
---

<footer class="bg-[#1C2822] text-white pt-16 pb-8 border-t border-[#2D3E35]/30">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
    
    <!-- Column 1: Brand Logo & Mission -->
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <a href="/" class="inline-block mb-6">
        <img src={logo.src} alt="Las Cabañas Logo" class="h-12 w-auto" loading="lazy" />
      </a>
      <p class="text-[#A2B6AC] text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Un refugio de paz y transformación en la naturaleza. Vive retiros y ceremonias ancestrales diseñadas para sanar y reconectar en el corazón de los Andes y la Amazonía.
      </p>
      
      <!-- Social Media Links -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2.5">
        <a 
          href="https://www.facebook.com/share/17Z6s3Q1K7/" 
          target="_blank" 
          aria-label="Facebook" 
          title="Facebook"
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-[#2D3E35] flex items-center justify-center text-[#A2B6AC] hover:text-white hover:bg-orange-400 hover:border-orange-400 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook-f text-sm"></i>
        </a>
        <a 
          href="https://www.instagram.com/ecolodgecabanas?utm_source=qr&igsh=OXl6MGFiNTRkcDZx" 
          target="_blank" 
          aria-label="Instagram Cabañas" 
          title="Instagram Cabañas"
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-[#2D3E35] flex items-center justify-center text-[#A2B6AC] hover:text-white hover:bg-orange-400 hover:border-orange-400 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram text-sm"></i>
        </a>
        <a 
          href="https://www.instagram.com/retirosrenace?utm_source=qr&igsh=MXNjMjJma2p4b3lnOA==" 
          target="_blank" 
          aria-label="Instagram Retiros Renace" 
          title="Instagram Retiros Renace"
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-[#2D3E35] flex items-center justify-center text-[#A2B6AC] hover:text-white hover:bg-orange-400 hover:border-orange-400 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <div class="relative">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram text-sm"></i>
            <span class="absolute -top-1.5 -right-1.5 bg-orange-400 text-white text-[7px] w-3 h-3 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold border border-[#1C2822]" title="Retiros Renace">R</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a 
          href="https://www.tiktok.com/@ecolodgecabanasurubamba?_r=1&_t=ZS-97BkfpUorGn" 
          target="_blank" 
          aria-label="TikTok" 
          title="TikTok"
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-[#2D3E35] flex items-center justify-center text-[#A2B6AC] hover:text-white hover:bg-orange-400 hover:border-orange-400 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <i class="fa-brands fa-tiktok text-sm"></i>
        </a>
        <a 
          href="https://www.airbnb.mx/rooms/29439580?unique_share_id=60ee8375-1c1e-4908-9f4e-7f04c983e865&viralityEntryPoint=1&s=76" 
          target="_blank" 
          aria-label="Airbnb" 
          title="Airbnb"
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-[#2D3E35] flex items-center justify-center text-[#A2B6AC] hover:text-white hover:bg-orange-400 hover:border-orange-400 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <i class="fa-brands fa-airbnb text-sm"></i>
        </a>
        <a 
          href="https://www.booking.com/Share-5Szggc" 
          target="_blank" 
          aria-label="Booking.com" 
          title="Booking.com"
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-[#2D3E35] flex items-center justify-center text-[#A2B6AC] hover:text-white hover:bg-orange-400 hover:border-orange-400 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M2.5 0h19A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 24 2.5v19a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-2.5 2.5h-19A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0 21.5v-19A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 2.5 0zm6.9 4c-.7 0-1.2.6-1.2 1.3V18.7c0 .7.5 1.3 1.2 1.3h5.4c2.8 0 4.7-1.4 4.7-4.1 0-1.7-.9-2.9-2.5-3.3 1.3-.5 2-1.7 2-3.1 0-2.5-1.8-3.5-4.4-3.5H9.4zm2.8 2.8h2.3c1 0 1.6.3 1.6 1.1s-.6 1.1-1.6 1.1h-2.3V6.8zm0 4.9h2.5c1.1 0 1.8.4 1.8 1.3s-.7 1.3-1.8 1.3h-2.5v-2.6z"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a 
          href="https://wa.link/ngq3h9" 
          target="_blank" 
          aria-label="WhatsApp" 
          title="WhatsApp"
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-[#2D3E35] flex items-center justify-center text-[#A2B6AC] hover:text-white hover:bg-orange-400 hover:border-orange-400 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-sm"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Column 2: Sedes (Locations) -->
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-6 tracking-tight relative after:content-[''] after:absolute after:bottom-[-8px] after:left-0 after:w-8 after:h-0.5 after:bg-orange-400">
        Nuestras Sedes
      </h3>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-[#A2B6AC]">
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot text-orange-400 mt-1"></i>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Urubamba</h4>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">El bosque de Tacllanca, a 10 min de la plaza de Urubamba, Valle Sagrado.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot text-orange-400 mt-1"></i>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Cusco</h4>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">Urb. Vera Velasco, vía de evitamiento, a 5 min del aeropuerto, San Sebastián.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot text-orange-400 mt-1"></i>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Tingo María</h4>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">Montañas de San Juan de Cocheros (desvío Huachipa), a 1:45 h de Tingo María.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Column 3: Quick Links -->
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-6 tracking-tight relative after:content-[''] after:absolute after:bottom-[-8px] after:left-0 after:w-8 after:h-0.5 after:bg-orange-400">
        Enlaces Rápidos
      </h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-[#A2B6AC]">
        <li>
          <a href="/" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center gap-1">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[10px] opacity-50"></i> Inicio
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/urubamba-valle-sagrado" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center gap-1">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[10px] opacity-50"></i> Cabañas Valle Sagrado
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/tingo-maria" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center gap-1">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[10px] opacity-50"></i> Cabañas Tingo María
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/cusco" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center gap-1">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[10px] opacity-50"></i> Cabañas Cusco
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/retiros" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center gap-1 font-medium text-white/95">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[10px] text-orange-400"></i> Retiros y Ceremonias
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/campamentos-conscientes" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center gap-1">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[10px] opacity-50"></i> Campamentos
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/galeria" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center gap-1">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[10px] opacity-50"></i> Galería
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Column 4: Contact & Action -->
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-6 tracking-tight relative after:content-[''] after:absolute after:bottom-[-8px] after:left-0 after:w-8 after:h-0.5 after:bg-orange-400">
        Contáctanos
      </h3>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-[#A2B6AC]">
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          ¿Tienes preguntas o deseas reservar una experiencia? Contáctanos de inmediato:
        </p>
        <a 
          href="tel:+51984746645" 
          class="flex items-center gap-3 hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors duration-200 text-white font-medium"
        >
          <i class="fa-solid fa-phone text-orange-400 text-xs"></i> +51 984 746 645
        </a>
        <a 
          href="mailto:ecolodgelascabanas@gmail.com" 
          class="flex items-center gap-3 hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors duration-200 break-all text-white font-medium"
        >
          <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope text-orange-400 text-xs"></i> ecolodgelascabanas@gmail.com
        </a>
        <div class="pt-2">
          <a 
            href="https://wa.link/ngq3h9" 
            target="_blank" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-orange-400 hover:bg-orange-500 text-white text-xs font-bold rounded-lg shadow-md transition-all duration-300 uppercase tracking-wider w-full"
            aria-label="Contact via WhatsApp"
          >
            <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-sm"></i> WhatsApp Online
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Copyright Bottom Bar -->
  <div class="border-t border-[#2D3E35]/40 mt-12 pt-8 text-center text-xs text-[#8BA498]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
      <p>
        &copy; 2025 Ecolodge Cabañas y Retiros. Todos los derechos reservados. | RUC: 10240034587.
      </p>
      <p class="flex items-center gap-1">
        Hecho con <i class="fa-solid fa-heart text-red-500 text-[10px]"></i> en el Valle Sagrado.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>